---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
import Breadcrumbs from '../components/Breadcrumbs.astro';
---

<Layout
  title="Cookie Policy | Baltimore Wedding Planner"
  description="How Baltimore Wedding Planner uses cookies and tracking technologies. Details on analytics cookies and how to manage your preferences."
  canonical="https://baltimoreweddingplanner.com/cookie-policy"
  noindex={true}
>
  <div class="container">
    <Breadcrumbs items={[{ label: 'Cookie Policy' }]} />
  </div>

  <section class="section bg-[#FAF7F5]">
    <div class="container max-w-3xl">

      <div class="mb-10">
        <h1 class="font-display text-3xl md:text-4xl font-semibold text-stone-900 tracking-tight mb-3">Cookie Policy</h1>
        <p class="text-stone-500 text-sm font-body">Effective Date: June 4, 2026 | Last Updated: June 4, 2026</p>
      </div>

      <div class="prose prose-stone max-w-none font-body text-stone-600 font-light leading-relaxed space-y-8">

        <div>
          <h2 class="font-display text-xl font-semibold text-stone-900 mb-3">What Are Cookies?</h2>
          <p>Cookies are small text files stored on your device when you visit a website. They help sites remember information about your visit, which can make your experience more consistent and the site easier to use.</p>
          <p class="mt-3">We also use similar technologies like local storage and session storage for some purposes.</p>
        </div>

        <div>
          <h2 class="font-display text-xl font-semibold text-stone-900 mb-3">Cookies We Use</h2>

          <h3 class="font-display text-base font-semibold text-stone-800 mb-3 mt-4">Strictly Necessary</h3>
          <p class="text-sm mb-3">These cookies are required for the Site to function. They can't be disabled.</p>
          <div class="overflow-x-auto">
            <table class="w-full text-xs border-collapse">
              <thead>
                <tr class="bg-stone-100">
                  <th class="text-left p-3 font-semibold text-stone-900 border border-stone-200">Cookie</th>
                  <th class="text-left p-3 font-semibold text-stone-900 border border-stone-200">Duration</th>
                  <th class="text-left p-3 font-semibold text-stone-900 border border-stone-200">Purpose</th>
                </tr>
              </thead>
              <tbody>
                <tr><td class="p-3 border border-stone-200">bwp_consent</td><td class="p-3 border border-stone-200">1 year</td><td class="p-3 border border-stone-200">Stores your cookie consent preferences</td></tr>
              </tbody>
            </table>
          </div>

          <h3 class="font-display text-base font-semibold text-stone-800 mb-3 mt-6">Analytics Cookies</h3>
          <p class="text-sm mb-3">These cookies help us understand how visitors use our Site. All data is anonymized. These cookies are only set with your consent.</p>
          <div class="overflow-x-auto">
            <table class="w-full text-xs border-collapse">
              <thead>
                <tr class="bg-stone-100">
                  <th class="text-left p-3 font-semibold text-stone-900 border border-stone-200">Cookie</th>
                  <th class="text-left p-3 font-semibold text-stone-900 border border-stone-200">Provider</th>
                  <th class="text-left p-3 font-semibold text-stone-900 border border-stone-200">Duration</th>
                  <th class="text-left p-3 font-semibold text-stone-900 border border-stone-200">Purpose</th>
                </tr>
              </thead>
              <tbody>
                <tr><td class="p-3 border border-stone-200">_ga</td><td class="p-3 border border-stone-200">Google Analytics</td><td class="p-3 border border-stone-200">2 years</td><td class="p-3 border border-stone-200">Distinguishes users for analytics</td></tr>
                <tr class="bg-stone-50"><td class="p-3 border border-stone-200">_ga_*</td><td class="p-3 border border-stone-200">Google Analytics</td><td class="p-3 border border-stone-200">2 years</td><td class="p-3 border border-stone-200">Persists session state</td></tr>
                <tr><td class="p-3 border border-stone-200">_clck</td><td class="p-3 border border-stone-200">Microsoft Clarity</td><td class="p-3 border border-stone-200">1 year</td><td class="p-3 border border-stone-200">Persists Clarity User ID</td></tr>
                <tr class="bg-stone-50"><td class="p-3 border border-stone-200">_clsk</td><td class="p-3 border border-stone-200">Microsoft Clarity</td><td class="p-3 border border-stone-200">1 day</td><td class="p-3 border border-stone-200">Connects multiple page views in a session</td></tr>
                <tr><td class="p-3 border border-stone-200">MUID</td><td class="p-3 border border-stone-200">Microsoft Clarity</td><td class="p-3 border border-stone-200">1 year</td><td class="p-3 border border-stone-200">Microsoft user identifier</td></tr>
              </tbody>
            </table>
          </div>

          <h3 class="font-display text-base font-semibold text-stone-800 mb-3 mt-6">Third-Party Cookies (Functionality)</h3>
          <p class="text-sm mb-3">These cookies are set by third-party services embedded on our Site when you interact with them.</p>
          <div class="overflow-x-auto">
            <table class="w-full text-xs border-collapse">
              <thead>
                <tr class="bg-stone-100">
                  <th class="text-left p-3 font-semibold text-stone-900 border border-stone-200">Service</th>
                  <th class="text-left p-3 font-semibold text-stone-900 border border-stone-200">Purpose</th>
                  <th class="text-left p-3 font-semibold text-stone-900 border border-stone-200">Their Policy</th>
                </tr>
              </thead>
              <tbody>
                <tr><td class="p-3 border border-stone-200">Calendly</td><td class="p-3 border border-stone-200">Consultation booking widget</td><td class="p-3 border border-stone-200">calendly.com/privacy</td></tr>
                <tr class="bg-stone-50"><td class="p-3 border border-stone-200">Google Fonts</td><td class="p-3 border border-stone-200">Typography delivery</td><td class="p-3 border border-stone-200">policies.google.com/privacy</td></tr>
              </tbody>
            </table>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div>
          <h2 class="font-display text-xl font-semibold text-stone-900 mb-3">Managing Your Cookie Preferences</h2>

          <h3 class="font-display text-base font-semibold text-stone-800 mb-2">Cookie Consent Banner</h3>
          <p>When you first visit our Site, you'll see a cookie consent banner. You can accept all cookies, reject non-essential cookies, or manage preferences individually. You can change your choice at any time by clicking "Cookie Preferences" in the footer.</p>

          <h3 class="font-display text-base font-semibold text-stone-800 mb-2 mt-5">Browser Settings</h3>
          <p>You can control cookies through your browser settings:</p>
          <ul class="list-disc pl-6 mt-2 space-y-1 text-sm">
            <li><strong>Chrome:</strong> Settings &gt; Privacy and security &gt; Cookies and other site data</li>
            <li><strong>Safari:</strong> Preferences &gt; Privacy</li>
            <li><strong>Firefox:</strong> Settings &gt; Privacy & Security</li>
            <li><strong>Edge:</strong> Settings &gt; Privacy, search, and services</li>
          </ul>
          <p class="mt-3 text-sm">Disabling all cookies may affect site functionality.</p>

          <h3 class="font-display text-base font-semibold text-stone-800 mb-2 mt-5">Opt-Out Links</h3>
          <ul class="list-disc pl-6 mt-2 space-y-1 text-sm">
            <li>Google Analytics: <a href="https://tools.google.com/dlpage/gaoptout" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="text-[#C89481] hover:underline">Google Analytics Opt-out</a></li>
            <li>Microsoft Clarity: <a href="https://privacy.microsoft.com/privacystatement" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="text-[#C89481] hover:underline">Microsoft Privacy Statement</a></li>
          </ul>
        </div>

        <div>
          <h2 class="font-display text-xl font-semibold text-stone-900 mb-3">Do Not Track</h2>
          <p>Some browsers offer a "Do Not Track" (DNT) signal. Our Site does not currently respond to DNT signals, but you can use our cookie consent banner to limit tracking.</p>
        </div>

        <div>
          <h2 class="font-display text-xl font-semibold text-stone-900 mb-3">Changes to This Policy</h2>
          <p>We may update this Cookie Policy when we add new tracking technologies or our practices change. The "Last Updated" date above reflects any changes.</p>
        </div>

        <div>
          <h2 class="font-display text-xl font-semibold text-stone-900 mb-3">Contact</h2>
          <p>For questions about our use of cookies: <a href="mailto:john@baltimoreweddingplanner.com" class="text-[#C89481] hover:underline">john@baltimoreweddingplanner.com</a></p>
          <p class="mt-2">Also see our <a href="/privacy-policy" class="text-[#C89481] hover:underline">Privacy Policy</a> for broader information about how we handle your data.</p>
        </div>

      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</Layout>
